public GeckoResult<Bitmap> get(int pixelSize)
        Get the best version of this icon for size pixelSize. Embedders are encouraged to cache the result of this method keyed with this instance.
        Parameters:
        pixelSize - pixel size at which this icon will be displayed at.

        A GeckoResult that resolves to the bitmap when ready.
